long.ar,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,fa,fil,hi,hu,:
❤️Learn better with ChatGPT 
💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
➡️ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
➡️ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
➡️ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:What is ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

❤️Learn better with ChatGPT 
💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
➡️ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
➡️ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
➡️ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:What is ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

🙋Fragen und Antworten
👉Q1: Was ist ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT ist ein von OpenAI entwickeltes Sprachmodell, das ein großes, vortrainiertes, transformatorbasiertes neuronales Netzwerk verwendet, um menschenähnlichen Text als Reaktion auf Benutzereingaben zu generieren. Mit seinem vielfältigen Schulungsangebot zu Internettexten kann ChatGPT Antworten zu verschiedenen Themen wie Allgemeinwissen, Konversation und kreatives Schreiben geben.

👉F2: Was ist die Google/YouTube-Zusammenfassung mit ChatGPT?
🚀A2: Es ist eine Erweiterung, die gleichzeitig eine Zusammenfassung von ChatGPT in den Google-Suchergebnissen anzeigt. Außerdem können Sie auch eine Zusammenfassung der YouTube-Videos erhalten.

👉Q3: Ist die Google/YouTube-Zusammenfassung mit ChatGPT kostenlos?
🚀Q3: Obwohl unsere Erweiterung derzeit kostenlos ist, prüfen wir die Möglichkeit, eine kleine Paywall einzuführen, um den Service in Zukunft aufrechtzuerhalten. Durch das Upgrade auf den kostenpflichtigen Service genießen Sie schnellere Reaktionszeiten, uneingeschränkten Zugriff und Kundensupport mit hoher Priorität. Unser oberstes Ziel ist es, Ihnen den bestmöglichen Service auf eine Weise zu bieten, die erschwinglich und für jedermann zugänglich ist.

👉Q4: Muss ich ein ChatGPT/OpenAI-Konto erstellen, um diese Erweiterung zu verwenden?
🚀Q4: Ja, Sie müssen über ein ChatGPT-Konto verfügen, um diese Erweiterung verwenden zu können. Sie können ein kostenloses Konto auf chat.openai.com erstellen.

❤️Learn better with ChatGPT 
💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
➡️ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
➡️ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
➡️ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:What is ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

long.fr:
❤️Apprenez mieux avec ChatGPT
💫Comment l'utiliser ?
➡️ Après avoir installé cette extension, elle passera à l'option Page. Vous pouvez sélectionner et définir le fournisseur d'API
➡️ Si vous avez tendance à utiliser ChatGPT Webapp comme fournisseur d'IA, c'est gratuit mais parfois instable, et mentionnez "Veuillez vous connecter et passer Cloudflare".
➡️ Nous vous recommandons donc d'utiliser votre propre clé API OpenAI. Comment obtenir votre propre clé API OpenAI ?
➡️ Connectez-vous https://platform.openai.com puis cliquez sur votre paramètre de compte personnel, vous pouvez voir "Afficher les clés API". Enfin, créez une nouvelle clé secrète ou copiez la clé que vous avez créée auparavant.
➡️ Collez votre clé API OpenAI dans le fournisseur AI et enregistrez votre configuration. Vous pouvez maintenant obtenir le résumé à côté des résultats de recherche Google ou du résumé des vidéos Youtube.

🙋Q&R
👉Q1 :Qu'est-ce que ChatGPT ?
🚀A1:ChatGPT est un modèle de langage développé par OpenAI qui utilise un vaste réseau neuronal pré-formé basé sur Transformer pour générer du texte de type humain en réponse aux invites de l'utilisateur. Avec sa gamme diversifiée de formations sur le texte Internet, ChatGPT peut fournir des réponses sur divers sujets, tels que les connaissances générales, les conversations et l'écriture créative.

👉Q2 :Qu'est-ce que le résumé Google/YouTube avec ChatGPT ?
🚀A2 : Il s'agit d'une extension qui affiche simultanément un résumé de ChatGPT dans les résultats de recherche Google. De plus, vous pouvez également obtenir un résumé des vidéos YouTube.

👉Q3 :Le résumé Google/YouTube avec ChatGPT est-il gratuit ?
🚀Q3 :Bien que notre extension soit actuellement gratuite, nous étudions la possibilité d'introduire un petit paywall pour maintenir le service à l'avenir. En passant au service payant, vous bénéficierez de temps de réponse plus rapides, d'un accès illimité et d'un support client hautement prioritaire. Notre objectif ultime est de vous fournir le meilleur service possible d'une manière abordable et accessible à tous.

👉Q4 : Dois-je créer un compte ChatGPT/OpenAI pour utiliser cette extension ?
🚀Q4 :Oui, vous devez avoir un compte ChatGPT pour utiliser cette extension. Vous pouvez créer un compte gratuit sur chat.openai.com.

❤️Impara meglio con ChatGPT
💫Come si usa?
➡️ Dopo aver installato questa estensione, passerà alla pagina delle opzioni. È possibile selezionare e impostare il provider API
➡️ Se tendi a utilizzare ChatGPT Webapp come provider di intelligenza artificiale, è gratuito ma a volte instabile e menziona "Accedi e passa Cloudflare".
➡️ Quindi ti consigliamo di utilizzare la tua chiave API OpenAI. Come ottenere la tua chiave API OpenAI?
➡️ Accedi a https://platform.openai.com e poi fai clic sulle impostazioni del tuo account personale, puoi vedere "Visualizza chiavi API". Infine, crea una nuova chiave segreta o copia la chiave che hai creato in precedenza.
➡️ Incolla la tua chiave API OpenAI su AI Provider e salva la tua configurazione. Ora puoi ottenere il riepilogo insieme ai risultati di ricerca di Google o al riepilogo dei video di Youtube.

🙋Domande e risposte
👉D1: Cos'è ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT è un modello di linguaggio sviluppato da OpenAI che utilizza una grande rete neurale pre-addestrata basata su Transformer per generare testo simile a quello umano in risposta alle richieste dell'utente. Con la sua vasta gamma di formazione sul testo Internet, ChatGPT può fornire risposte su vari argomenti, come conoscenze generali, conversazioni e scrittura creativa.

👉Q2: Che cos'è Google/YouTube Summary con ChatGPT?
🚀A2: è un'estensione che visualizza contemporaneamente un riepilogo di ChatGPT nei risultati di ricerca di Google. Inoltre, puoi anche ottenere un riepilogo dei video di YouTube.

👉D3:Riepilogo Google/YouTube con ChatGPT è gratuito?
🚀Q3: Sebbene la nostra estensione sia attualmente gratuita, stiamo esplorando la possibilità di introdurre un piccolo paywall per sostenere il servizio in futuro. Eseguendo l'upgrade al servizio a pagamento, godrai di tempi di risposta più rapidi, accesso illimitato e assistenza clienti ad alta priorità. Il nostro obiettivo finale è fornire il miglior servizio possibile in un modo che sia conveniente e accessibile a tutti.

👉Q4: Devo creare un account ChatGPT/OpenAI per utilizzare questa estensione?
🚀D4: Sì, devi disporre di un account ChatGPT per utilizzare questa estensione. Puoi creare un account gratuito su chat.openai.com.

❤️ChatGPTでよりよく学ぶ
💫使い方は？
➡️ この拡張機能をインストールすると、オプションページにジャンプします。 APIプロバイダを選択して設定できます
➡️ AIプロバイダーとしてChatGPT Webアプリをよく利用する場合は、無料ですが不安定な場合があり、「ログインしてCloudflareをパスしてください」と伝えてください。
➡️ 独自の OpenAI API キーを使用することをお勧めします。 独自の OpenAI API キーを取得するには?
➡️ https://platform.openai.com にログインし、個人アカウントの設定をクリックすると、「View API keys」が表示されます。最後に、新しいシークレット キーを作成するか、以前に作成したキーをコピーします。
➡️ OpenAI API キーを AI プロバイダーに貼り付け、構成を保存します。Google 検索結果または Youtube ビデオの概要と一緒に概要を取得できます。

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:ChatGPTとは？
🚀A1:ChatGPT は OpenAI が開発した言語モデルで、事前トレーニング済みの大規模な Transformer ベースのニューラル ネットワークを利用して、ユーザーのプロンプトに応じて人間のようなテキストを生成します。 ChatGPT は、インターネット テキストに関するさまざまなトレーニングを備えているため、一般的な知識、会話、クリエイティブ ライティングなど、さまざまなトピックに関する回答を提供できます。

👉Q2:ChatGPTでGoogle/YouTubeのまとめとは？
🚀A2:ChatGPTのまとめをGoogle検索結果に同時に表示する拡張機能です。また、YouTube動画のまとめも取得できます。

👉Q3:ChatGPT での Google/YouTube の概要は無料ですか?
🚀Q3:拡張機能は現在無料ですが、将来的にサービスを維持するために小さなペイウォールを導入する可能性を探っています。 有料サービスにアップグレードすることで、より迅速な応答時間、無制限のアクセス、優先度の高いカスタマー サポートを享受できます。 私たちの究極の目標は、誰もが手頃な価格でアクセスできる方法で、可能な限り最高のサービスを提供することです.

👉Q4:この拡張機能を使用するには、ChatGPT/OpenAI アカウントを作成する必要がありますか?
🚀Q4:はい、この拡張機能を使用するには ChatGPT アカウントが必要です。 chat.openai.com で無料のアカウントを作成できます。

❤️ChatGPT로 더 잘 알아보기
💫사용방법은?
➡️ 이 확장 프로그램을 설치하면 옵션 페이지로 이동합니다. API Provider를 선택하고 설정할 수 있습니다.
➡️ ChatGPT Webapp을 AI 공급자로 사용하는 경향이 있는 경우 무료이지만 때때로 불안정하며 "로그인하고 Cloudflare를 통과하십시오"라고 언급하십시오.
➡️ 따라서 자체 OpenAI API 키를 사용하는 것이 좋습니다. 자신의 OpenAI API 키를 얻는 방법은 무엇입니까?
➡️ https://platform.openai.com 로그인 후 개인 계정 설정을 클릭하면 "API 키 보기"가 표시됩니다. 마지막으로 새 비밀 키를 생성하거나 이전에 생성한 키를 복사합니다.
➡️ OpenAI API 키를 AI 공급자에 붙여넣고 구성을 저장합니다. 지금 Google 검색 결과 또는 Youtube 비디오 요약과 함께 요약을 얻을 수 있습니다.

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:ChatGPT가 무엇인가요?
🚀A1:ChatGPT는 사용자 프롬프트에 대한 응답으로 사람과 유사한 텍스트를 생성하기 위해 대규모 사전 훈련된 Transformer 기반 신경망을 활용하는 OpenAI 개발 언어 모델입니다. 인터넷 텍스트에 대한 다양한 교육을 통해 ChatGPT는 일반 지식, 대화 및 창의적 글쓰기와 같은 다양한 주제에 대한 답변을 제공할 수 있습니다.

👉Q2:ChatGPT로 Google/YouTube 요약이 무엇인가요?
🚀A2:Google 검색 결과에 ChatGPT 요약을 동시에 표시하는 확장 프로그램입니다. 또한 YouTube 동영상 요약도 얻을 수 있습니다.

👉Q3:Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT는 무료인가요?
🚀Q3:현재 확장 프로그램은 무료이지만 향후 서비스를 유지하기 위해 작은 페이월을 도입할 가능성을 모색하고 있습니다. 유료 서비스로 업그레이드하면 더 빠른 응답 시간, 무제한 액세스 및 최우선 고객 지원을 누릴 수 있습니다. 우리의 궁극적인 목표는 모든 사람이 저렴하고 접근할 수 있는 방식으로 최상의 서비스를 제공하는 것입니다.

👉Q4:이 확장 프로그램을 사용하려면 ChatGPT/OpenAI 계정을 만들어야 하나요?
🚀Q4:네, 이 확장 프로그램을 사용하려면 ChatGPT 계정이 있어야 합니다. chat.openai.com에서 무료 계정을 만들 수 있습니다.

❤️Learn better with ChatGPT 
💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
➡️ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
➡️ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
➡️ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:What is ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

❤️Learn better with ChatGPT 
💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
➡️ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
➡️ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
➡️ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:What is ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

❤️Learn better with ChatGPT 
💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
➡️ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
➡️ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
➡️ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:What is ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

❤️Learn better with ChatGPT 
💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
➡️ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
➡️ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
➡️ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:What is ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

💫How to use it?
➡️ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
➡️ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
➡️ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
➡️ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
➡️ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

🙋Q&A
👉Q1:What is ChatGPT?
🚀A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

👉Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
🚀A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

👉Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
🚀Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

👉Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
🚀Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

❤️通过 ChatGPT 更好地学习
💫如何使用？
➡️ 安装此扩展程序后，它会跳转到选项页面。 您可以选择和设置 API Provider
➡️ 如果您倾向于使用 ChatGPT Webapp 作为 AI Provider，它是免费的但有时不稳定，并提及您“请登录并通过 Cloudflare”。
➡️ 所以我们建议您使用自己的 OpenAI API 密钥。 如何获得自己的 OpenAI API 密钥？
➡️登录https://platform.openai.com 然后点击你的个人账户设置，你可以看到“查看API密钥”。最后创建一个新的密钥或者复制你之前创建的密钥。
➡️ 将您的 OpenAI API 密钥粘贴到 AI Provider 并保存您的配置。您现在可以在 Google 搜索结果或 Youtube 视频摘要旁边获取摘要。

🙋问答
👉Q1:ChatGPT 是什么？
🚀A1：ChatGPT 是一种由 OpenAI 开发的语言模型，它利用大型预训练的基于 Transformer 的神经网络来响应用户提示生成类似人类的文本。 ChatGPT 凭借其多样化的互联网文本培训，可以提供各种主题的回复，例如常识、对话和创意写作。

👉Q2: 什么是 Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT？
🚀A2：这是一个在谷歌搜索结果中同时显示ChatGPT摘要的扩展。此外，您还可以获得YouTube视频的摘要。

👉Q3:Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT 免费吗？
🚀Q3：虽然我们的扩展目前是免费的，但我们正在探索引入一个小的付费墙来维持未来服务的可能性。 通过升级到付费服务，您将享受到更快的响应时间、不受限制的访问和高优先级的客户支持。 我们的最终目标是以每个人都负担得起且易于使用的方式为您提供最好的服务。

👉Q4:我需要创建一个ChatGPT/OpenAI账户才能使用这个扩展吗？
🚀Q4:是的，您必须拥有 ChatGPT 帐户才能使用此扩展程序。 您可以在 chat.openai.com 创建一个免费帐户。
